summary: i’m not really a soft or sensitive person in general but i actually became much more of a hardass as a defense mechanism. i’ve...
body: i’m not really a soft or sensitive person in general but i actually became much more of a hardass as a defense mechanism. i’ve broken down many of those walls since then, but i just want to thank dan howell for having the strength to grow and change on camera bc doing that shit off camera was challenging enough. being a softie means being vulnerable, and even though i can’t qualify myself as the personality equivalent of a fluff ball, being able to soften up is so valuable. dan howell is such a brave boy
